text: Þis sindon þa landgemæro to austan.
Ærest of sæfern & swa forð be tatan grafes wurt wale.
And þonne swa forð<../images/tbar.gif>hit sticað on miclan cumb.
And of miclan cumbe<../images/tbar.gif>hit sticað on litlan cumb.
And of litlan cumbe<../images/tbar.gif>on irfurlanges dic.
And of irfurlanges dic<../images/tbar.gif>on mær dic.
And of bradan bricge<../images/tbar.gif>on holan pyl.
And of holan pylle on wincan hammes dic.
And of wincan hammes dic innan miclan pyl.
And of miclan pylle<../images/tbar.gif>æft on sæferne.
